c-e61caffd7318&ssb=kdg4ezad5bmihd1i0p6zz0zlp&ssc=https%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Fabstract%2F0004-637X%2F669%2F2%2F1279&ssd=042435949607606&sse=h%40%40gadhnpchipjm&ssf=0ebaa85cfea3e449555da30c330c23c78deac756&ssg=3ccf46d0-e2da-485c-b994-a60be0f5c09e&ssh=d524a08e-8011-42b2-84b9-df4468ce6c8e&ssi=169f1231-8427-459c-a487-b986a12f2168&ssj=3e17dbfd-032c-4131-ba64-656bc4442c11&ssk=support%40shieldsquare.com&ssl=056528528992&ssm=94129928409763868226753274953621&ssn=3a265fa1a8834c77dd50f8236aabb19e5fc2bc0fa2eb-7cbd-4965-869498&sso=6a5d00e8-3385e116c61e8a14ed059e8edc986d6f566bc89687883b23&ssp=47948385001576229938157621992778737&ssq=81832464319893467427302989694898349815625&ssr=MjA3LjI0MS4yMzIuMTIx&sss=Mozilla%2F4.0%20%28compatible%3B%20MSIE%208.0%3B%20Windows%20NT%206.1%29%20Gecko%2F20100101%20Firefox%2F39.0&sst=Python-urllib%2F2.7&ssu=Chrome%2F5.0%20%28iPhone%3B%20U%3B%20CPU%20iPhone%20OS%203_0%20like%20Mac%20OS%20X%3B%20en-us%29%20AppleWebKit%2F528.18%20%28KHTML%2C%20like%20Gecko%29%20Version%2F4.0%20Mobile%2F7A341%20Safari%2F528.16&ssv=p23npvu3noosvnl&ssw=&ssx=570633000263890&ssy=amaeinic%40ccoljjkaopokcfbcelhlmkijink%40jmp&ssz=eee9742843f9007 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 随着[[开普勒太空望远镜|开普勒任务]]的进行，很多类似行星将会不断被发现，比如最近发现海洋星球的候选人[[开普勒22b|开普勒22b]]。系外行星[[格利泽581d|格利泽581d]]也可能是一颗海洋行星，它位于[[格利泽581|格利泽581]]的[[适居带|适居带]]内。该行星上的[[温室效应|温室效应]]使得行星温度适于液态水的存在。

